\begin_inset Formula $f_{x_{i_{1}}x_{i_{2}}\cdots x_{i_{k}}}\coloneqq\partial_{x_{i_{1}}}\partial_{x_{i_{2}}}\cdots\partial_{x_{i_{k}}}f$
\end_inset

, donde los 
\begin_inset Formula $i_{j}$
