=\left(v_{rr}-\cancel{2u_{xy}\cos\theta\sen\theta}\right)+\left(\frac{1}{r^{2}}v_{\t\t}-\left(-\cancel{2u_{xy}\cos\t\sen\t}-\frac{1}{r}\left(u_{x}\cos\t+u_{y}\sen\t\right)\right)\right)=\\
